metadata.description: Comprehensive head-to-head comparison of CRND against 11 baselines (kDN, cleanlab, k-NN consistency, random) across 5 datasets, 3 noise rates, and multiple seeds.
metadata.note_knn_consist_equals_kdn: knn_consist_* scores are numerically identical to kdn_* per exp_id3 metadata. Excluded from unique comparisons.

examples.input: CRND vs 8 baselines on medical_abstracts at 0.05 noise rate. CRND (10 seeds): AUC=0.51100.0297, rho=0.00830.0224
examples.output: Best baseline: cleanlab_avg AUC=0.89360.0123. Delta AUC (CRND-best)=-0.3826
